e.</li><li>Managed multi-repo codebases on GitHub with standardized PR reviews and automation.</li><li>Mentored junior developers, enforced best practices, and led roadmap execution with founders.</li></ul></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Colliers International (via TopCoder) — Remote</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Full-stack Developer</span><span>Oct 2021 – Sep 2023</span></div></div><p class="summary">Modernized internal apps for a global commercial real-estate firm, replacing third-party tools with Azure-native and AWS-native services.</p><ul class="bulletList"><li>Replaced a 3rd-party valuation tool with an internal AWS solution (EC2, S3, SES, RDS) in 3 weeks; cut vendor cost ~60–80% and absorbed additional developer cost solo.</li><li>Architected microservices on Azure Functions backed by Cosmos DB + SQL Server; reduced API p95 latency ~30–50%.</li><li>Implemented IaC + CI/CD with Terraform and Azure DevOps.</li><li>Mentored engineers and led POCs with architects/BAs; reduced new-hire ramp ~30–50% and accelerated concept-to-pilot ~2x.</li><li>Drove code reviews and onboarding standards; PR cycle time −20–35%, post-release defects −20–40%.</li></ul></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Relisource Inc. — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Nov 2018 – Aug 2021</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Actively mentored team members on architecture and clean code practices.</li></ul></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Astha IT — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Mar 2014 – Oct 2018</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Led development for enterprise systems in logistics, education, and fintech.</li><li>Mentored junior engineers and participated in system arch