a global pharmaceutical client.</li><li>Actively mentored team members on architecture and clean code practices.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">ASP.NET Core, Azure Functions, Azure Service Bus, Microsoft SQL Server</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Astha IT — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Mar 2014 – Oct 2018</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Led development for enterprise systems in logistics, education, and fintech.</li><li>Mentored junior engineers and participated in system architecture, client demos, and delivery cycles.</li></ul></article></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Projects</h2><div class="entry break-avoid"><div><span class="name">FinSync — Personal Finance Intelligence</span><a class="url" href="https://devpost.com/software/finsync-ai-powered-financial-assistant" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">↗</a></div><p class="desc">Elastic Serverless data streams + Vertex AI. Hybrid search (keyword + vector), monthly transforms, and a RAG chat layer. Pydantic-validated JSON ingestion.</p></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Education</h2><div class="entry"><div class="degree">Bachelor of Computer Science and Engineering</div><div class="line">Shahjalal University of Science and Technology · 2013</div></div></section></article>"`;

