2023 – May 2025</span></div></div><p class="summary">Led architecture and platform engineering for two SaaS products: an onboarding/automation platform and an A/V enhancement workflow service.</p><ul class="bulletList"><li>Built a public content-sharing system with Astro + Cloudflare Durable Objects; optimized for SEO and low global latency.</li><li>Developed a modular onboarding SDK (Shadow DOM → Lit Web Components) and a lightweight Chrome extension to test/debug onboarding flows.</li><li>Managed multi-repo codebases on GitHub with standardized PR reviews and automation.</li><li>Mentored junior developers, enforced best practices, and led roadmap execution with founders.</li><li>Integrated Clerk authentication across multiple applications.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">TypeScript, JavaScript, Node.js, React, Remix, Lit, Astro, Next.js</div><div class="techGroup">AWS (Lambda, EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront), Cloudflare (Workers, Durable Objects, R2)</div><div class="techGroup">PostHog, Datadog, CloudWatch, GitHub Actions, Docker</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Colliers International (via TopCoder) — Remote</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Full-stack Developer</span><span>Oct 2021 – Sep 2023</span></div></div><p class="summary">Modernized internal apps for a global commercial real-estate firm, replacing third-party tools with Azure-native and AWS-native services.</p><ul class="bulletList"><li>Modernized Angular apps (major version upgrades + module refactors); build time reduced 25–40%, unit test coverage to 90%.</li><li>Migrated Google Maps → Mapbox, added static-map support for exported documents.</li><li>Mentored engineers and led POCs with architects/BAs; reduced new-hire ramp ~30–50% and accelerated concept-to-pilot ~2x.</li><li>Drove code reviews and onboarding standards; PR cycle time −20–35%, post-release defects −20–40%.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">Angular, TypeScript</div><div class="techGroup">GraphQL, Power BI, Mapbox, Syncfusion</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Relisource Inc. — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Nov 2018 – Aug 2021</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Actively mentored team members on architecture and clean code practices.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">TypeScript, Angular, AngularJS</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Astha IT — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Mar 2014 – Oct 2018</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Led development for enterprise systems in logistics, education, and fintech.</li><li>Mentored junior engineers and participated in system architecture, client demos, and delivery cycles.</li></ul></article></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Education</h2><div class="entry"><div class="degree">Bachelor of Computer Science and Engineering</div><div class="line">Shahjalal University of Science and Technology · 2013</div></div></section></article>"`;

