exports[`templates × roles snapshots > fullstack / classic renders stable HTML 1`] = `"<article class="page"><div class="headerWrap"><header class="header "><div class="left"><h1 class="name ">S M Nowshadur Rahaman</h1><div class="title ">Senior Full-Stack Engineer</div></div><div class="contact "><span class="contactLine">+880 1851 836744</span><span class="contactLine"><a href="mailto:nowshad.rahaman@gmail.com">nowshad.rahaman@gmail.com</a></span><span class="contactLine">Rampura, Dhaka, Bangladesh</span><span class="contactLine"><span><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dashu-baba" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></span><span><span class="contactSep">·</span><a href="https://github.com/dashu-baba" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></span><span><span class="contactSep">·</span><a href="https://www.topcoder.com/members/dashu-baba" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TopCoder</a></span></span></div></header></div><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Professional Overview</h2><p class="body">Hands-on architect with over 11+ years of experience developing scalable, cloud-native platforms across startups and enterprises. Specializes in JavaScript/TypeScript, .NET, distributed systems, serverless architecture, and real-time data pipelines. Proven leadership in architecting platforms, driving cross-functional teams, and managing the DevOps lifecycle.</p></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Core Competencies</h2><div class="list"><div class="row"><b>Architecture:</b>Microservices, Serverless, CQRS, SaaS Platforms, Edge-first Design</div><div class="row"><b>Cloud Platforms:</b>AWS (Lambda, EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront, SNS, SES), Azure (Functions, Blob, Cosmos DB), Cloudflare (R2, KV, Durable Objects)</div><div class="row"><b>Languages:</b>JavaScript, TypeScript, C#, Python, Java, Go, SQL</div><div class="row"><b>Frontend:</b>React, Remix, Angular, Lit, Astro</div><div class="row"><b>Backend:</b>Node.js, .NET Core, Express, HonoJS, Next.js, FastAPI</div><div class="row"><b>Realtime:</b>Kafka, Redis, Supabase, RabbitMQ, Ably</div><div class="row"><b>Data:</b>Microsoft SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL, ClickHouse, Cosmos DB, DynamoDB</div><div class="row"><b>DevOps &amp; Observability:</b>CI/CD Pipelines, Docker, Terraform, GitHub Actions, Azure DevOps, Datadog (RUM, Tracing), CloudWatch, App Insights</div><div class="row"><b>Mobile:</b>Xamarin (Android), Flutter</div></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Professional Experience</h2><div class="list"><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">AdoptSequence &amp; AdoptIQ (Curtis Digital Inc.) — Remote</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Solution Architect</span><span>Oct 2023 – May 2025</span></div></div><p class="summary">Led architecture and platform engineering for two SaaS products: an onboarding/automation platform and an A/V enhancement workflow service.</p><ul class="bulletList"><li>Led backend migration of AdoptSequence from AWS Lambda → Trigger.dev to support long-running video processing.</li><li>Built a public content-sharing system with Astro + Cloudflare Durable Objects; optimized for SEO and low global latency.</li><li>Integrated Supabase for real-time sync and Postgres storage; replaced Ably, lowering latency and cost.</li><li>Operationalized RUM + APM in Datadog with CloudWatch signals; guided devs to review error patterns, improving iteration speed by ~50%.</li><li>Developed a modular onboarding SDK (Shadow DOM → Lit Web Components) and a lightweight Chrome extension to test/debug onboarding flows.</li><li>Managed multi-repo codebases on GitHub with standardized PR reviews and automation.</li><li>Mentored junior developers, enforced best practices, and led roadmap execution with founders.</li><li>Integrated Clerk authentication across multiple applications.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">TypeScript, JavaScript, Node.js, React, Remix, Lit, Astro, Next.js</div><div class="techGroup">AWS (Lambda, EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront), Cloudflare (Workers, Durable Objects, R2)</div><div class="techGroup">PostHog, Datadog, CloudWatch, GitHub Actions, Docker</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Colliers International (via TopCoder) — Remote</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Full-stack Developer</span><span>Oct 2021 – Sep 2023</span></div></div><p class="summary">Modernized internal apps for a global commercial real-estate firm, replacing third-party tools with Azure-native and AWS-native services.</p><ul class="bulletList"><li>Replaced a 3rd-party valuation tool with an internal AWS solution (EC2, S3, SES, RDS) in 3 weeks; cut vendor cost ~60–80% and absorbed additional developer cost solo.</li><li>Modernized Angular apps (major version upgrades + module refactors); build time reduced 25–40%, unit test coverage to 90%.</li><li>Migrated Google Maps → Mapbox, added static-map support for exported documents.</li><li>Mentored engineers and led POCs with architects/BAs; reduced new-hire ramp ~30–50% and accelerated concept-to-pilot ~2x.</li><li>Drove code reviews and onboarding standards; PR cycle time −20–35%, post-release defects −20–40%.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">Angular, TypeScript</div><div class="techGroup">GraphQL, Power BI, Mapbox, Syncfusion</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Relisource Inc. — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Nov 2018 – Aug 2021</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Developed a Clinical Trial Management System for a global pharmaceutical client.</li><li>Built an enterprise LMS platform with mobile support for educational clients.</li><li>Actively mentored team members on architecture and clean code practices.</li></ul><div class="techHeader">Tech Stack</div><div class="techGroup">TypeScript, Angular, AngularJS</div><div class="techGroup">Xamarin</div></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Astha IT — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Mar 2014 – Oct 2018</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Led development for enterprise systems in logistics, education, and fintech.</li><li>Mentored junior engineers and participated in system architecture, client demos, and delivery cycles.</li></ul></article></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Projects</h2><div class="entry break-avoid"><div><span class="name">FinSync — Personal Finance Intelligence</span><a class="url" href="https://devpost.com/software/finsync-ai-powered-financial-assistant" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">↗</a></div><p class="desc">Elastic Serverless data streams + Vertex AI. Hybrid search (keyword + vector), monthly transforms, and a RAG chat layer. Pydantic-validated JSON ingestion.</p></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Education</h2><div class="entry"><div class="degree">Bachelor of Computer Science and Engineering</div><div class="line">Shahjalal University of Science and Technology · 2013</div></div></section></article>"`;

