90%.</li><li>Migrated Google Maps → Mapbox, added static-map support for exported documents.</li><li>Mentored engineers and led POCs with architects/BAs; reduced new-hire ramp ~30–50% and accelerated concept-to-pilot ~2x.</li><li>Drove code reviews and onboarding standards; PR cycle time −20–35%, post-release defects −20–40%.</li></ul></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Relisource Inc. — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Nov 2018 – Aug 2021</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Actively mentored team members on architecture and clean code practices.</li></ul></article><article class="entry break-avoid"><div class="entryHead"><div class="company">Astha IT — Dhaka, Bangladesh</div><div class="meta"><span class="role">Senior Software Engineer</span><span>Mar 2014 – Oct 2018</span></div></div><ul class="bulletList"><li>Led development for enterprise systems in logistics, education, and fintech.</li><li>Mentored junior engineers and participated in system architecture, client demos, and delivery cycles.</li></ul></article></div></section><section><h2 class="sectionTitle ">Education</h2><div class="entry"><div class="degree">Bachelor of Computer Science and Engineering</div><div class="line">Shahjalal University of Science and Technology · 2013</div></div></section></article>"`;

